@startuml class-diagram-layered
' Biểu đồ tổng quan theo tầng — mỗi tầng chỉ hiện đại diện + ghi chú
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 25
skinparam ranksep 30
top to bottom direction

package "presentation\n(be/controllers)" as PRES #E8F4FD {
  together {
    class AuthController
    class OrderController
    class ReservationController
    class WaiterController
    class KitchenController
    class DashboardController
  }
  note right of AuthController
    **21 controller**
    user: Auth, Order, Reservation, Payment...
    admin: Waiter, Kitchen, Report, Branch...
    public: Tables (QR)
  end note
}

package "application\n(be/services)" as APP #FFF8E1 {
  together {
    class userService
    class reservationService
    class waiterService
    class kitchenService
    class paymentService
    class reportService
  }
  note right of userService
    **23 service module**
    Không có interface riêng.
    Chứa logic nghiệp vụ, transaction.
  end note
}

package "infrastructure\n(be/models, realtimeHub)" as INFRA #F3E5F5 {
  class SequelizeConnection <<db.js>>
  class SequelizeModels <<ORM + Repository>> {
    CRUD / transaction
  }
  class realtimeHub <<WebSocket>>
}

package "domain — entity\n(be/models)" as DOM #E8F5E9 {
  together {
    class Branch
    class User
    class Table
    class Reservation
    class Order
    class OrderItem
    class MenuItem
    class Payment
    class Employee
    class Review
    class OperationLog
  }
  note right of Branch
    **11 entity**
    Quan hệ khai báo tại models/index.js
  end note
}

package "crosscutting\n(middlewares, utils)" as CC #FFEBEE {
  together {
    class JwtService
    class Validator
    class AuthMiddleware
    class BranchScope
    class StatusConstants
  }
  note right of JwtService
    JWT, validate input, bcrypt,
    phân quyền chi nhánh, hằng số trạng thái
  end note
}

' ── Phụ thuộc giữa các tầng (một mũi tên / tầng) ──────────
PRES -down-> APP : gọi service
PRES -down-> INFRA : controller gọi ORM
APP -down-> INFRA : truy cập dữ liệu
INFRA -down-> DOM : map entity
PRES .down.> CC : dùng chung
APP .down.> CC : dùng chung

note as RULE
  **Nguyên tắc phụ thuộc**
  Presentation → Application → Infrastructure → Domain
  Crosscutting được dùng xuyên tầng (JWT, validate, status...)
  Domain không phụ thuộc tầng khác
end note

@enduml
